dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Gregory White. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Christina. Could you please provide me with your policy number? It should consist of six digits.
Sure, my policy number is five six eight seven two four.
Thank you, Christina. I also need your phone number for verification purposes. Could you please spell it out for me?
Of course, my phone number is eight six five, four two zero, nine one five six.
Thank you for providing the information, Christina. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that will be all. Thank you.
You're welcome, Christina. Thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
